Step-1:
---------
Download python install software from website

http://www.aixtools.net/index.php/python3
or
http://download.aixtools.net/tools/aixtools.python.py39.3.9.1.0.I


Step-2:
---------
ftp pyton install software "aixtools.python.py39.3.9.1.0.I" to path /tmp/pyinstall

Step-3:
-------

smit install
->  Install and Update Software
->  Install Software
->  INPUT device / directory for software </tmp/pyinstall>
->  SOFTWARE to install: aixtools.python3
->  ACCEPT new license agreements? yes

Press "ENTER" 2 times.

# cd /opt/bin
# ls -l

ln -sf /opt/bin/python3 /usr/bin/python
ls -l /usr/bin/python

lslpp -l | grep -i python (will show .adt, .rte, .man.en_US)

run the below commands

lslpp -h aixtools.python******.adt

lslpp -h aixtools.python******.rte

lslpp -h aixtools.python******.man.en_US

Step-4:
----------

check python is installed or not

$ python


oslevel -s

rpm -Uvh sudo-1.9* --nodeps

